# cancel()

**Instance Method**

Cancels an in-progress request for subscriber account information.

## Declaration

```swift
func cancel()
```

## Discussion

Your app uses this method to notify a [doc://com.apple.videosubscriberaccount/documentation/VideoSubscriberAccount/VSAccountManager] instance to cancel the current request for subscriber account information. No guarantees are made that the cancellation request will succeed or finish immediately.
